            <title>Mario &#038; Luigi RPG 完全新作　經典系列久違 9 年終於復活</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/19/mario-luigi-rpg-new/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mario-luigi-rpg-new</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/19/mario-luigi-rpg-new/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 16:28:56 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[nintendo direct]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Switch]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1244023</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>任天堂的瑪莉奧系列作品中，除了橫向或立體動作遊戲之外，還有不少玩法迴異的週邊作品，當中不乏佳作。最近他們就公佈了全新的《Mario &amp; Luigi RPG》遊戲，距離上作已經有 9 年時間。<br /><span id="more-1244023"></span></p><p>任天堂公佈，將會在 11 月 7 日推出全新《Mario &amp; Luigi RPG: Brotherhood》，一如系列之前的作品，遊戲將會是 RPG 解謎冒險形式，強調雙人合作的操控（Brother Action)，故事方面將會圍繞一個名為 Conetta 的角色（設計像是兩腳電源插頭），瑪裏奧和路易需要將他送回原本的世界。此外還有一隻豬型生物 Tabu 作陪伴，相信會在解謎時發揮作用。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_17183"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/b0PhKIMkB3A?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>這個系列最初在 2003 年推出，陸續推出了 5 個作品和兩個重製版，都是在手提遊戲機上的作品，由於有獨特的玩法和故事，一直受到不少人歡迎。今次整整等足 9 年才有新作，令不少原先以為系列已經完結的玩家相當興奮。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244024" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rpgnintendodirect202-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rpgnintendodirect202-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rpgnintendodirect202.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲ 遊戲講求兩個角色合作互動</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244026" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rpgnintendodirect202-2-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rpgnintendodirect202-2-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rpgnintendodirect202-2.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲ 世界觀依舊充滿玩味</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244027" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rpgnintendodirect202-3-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rpgnintendodirect202-3-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/rpgnintendodirect202-3.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲ 今次也是系列首次高清化，相信會有更好的故事體驗</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/06/shin-chan-shiro-of-coal-town/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【開箱】Switch《蠟筆小新，煤炭鎮的小白》限定版　附贈畫冊、黑膠碟詳細睇</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/09/civilization-vi-2025/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《文明帝國》系列新作明年推出　將登陸 Steam / PS / Xbox / Switch</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/07/switch-7/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">任天堂社長預告 Switch 後繼機將發布</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/19/mario-luigi-rpg-new/game-channel/">Mario &#038; Luigi RPG 完全新作　經典系列久違 9 年終於復活</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
