        <item>
            <title>勇者鬥惡龍 1-3 重製版公佈　HD-2D 風格保留懷舊像素人物</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/18/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/18/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:59:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Switch]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[勇者鬥惡龍]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1244016</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>經典遊戲重製版近年屢見不鮮，最近 Nintendo Direct 就公佈《勇者鬥惡龍》首三作的重製版，採用 3D 背景 + 2D 人物的混合風格，保持一定的懷舊感覺之餘又不失新鮮感。<br /><span id="more-1244016"></span></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_44248"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HRP0kpokbHQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>《勇者鬥惡龍》系列可説是日本 RPG 的頂級經典作品，其中首三作被稱為「羅德三部曲」，算是經典中的經典，人氣一直相當高。之前已經有傳聞指 Square Enix 將會推出 HD-2D 重製版的《勇者鬥惡龍 III》，在 Nintendo Direct 上就正式公佈，保留了原作的故事和玩法，不像 FF7 Remake 般完全提升畫面，而是用 2D 像素風格的人物結合 3D 精細背景和介面，讓玩家可以細味經典氣氛。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244017" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iiinintendodirect202-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iiinintendodirect202-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iiinintendodirect202.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲背景採用精緻的 3D 模型</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iiinintendodirect202-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iiinintendodirect202-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iiinintendodirect202-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲ 戰鬥畫面變成立體，不過人物繼續 2D</p><p>而之前 Square Enix 沒有透露的是，除了《勇者鬥惡龍 III》之外，《勇者鬥惡龍 I &amp; II》的 HD-2D 重製版也將會在明年發售，令「羅德三部曲」得以完整。《勇者鬥惡龍》製作人堀井雄二曾經表示，首三作的時間順序應該是 III &gt; I &gt; II，因此今次公佈首兩作將會在 2025 年推出，也剛好是符合了故事的時序。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244020" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240618298307001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240618298307001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240618298307001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這兩個重製版作品並非 Switch 獨佔，除了 Switch 之外，還會有 PlayStation 5、Xbox Series X|S 和 PC (Steam) 版本同步推出。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/06/shin-chan-shiro-of-coal-town/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【開箱】Switch《蠟筆小新，煤炭鎮的小白》限定版　附贈畫冊、黑膠碟詳細睇</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/09/civilization-vi-2025/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《文明帝國》系列新作明年推出　將登陸 Steam / PS / Xbox / Switch</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/07/switch-7/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">任天堂社長預告 Switch 後繼機將發布</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/18/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d/game-channel/">勇者鬥惡龍 1-3 重製版公佈　HD-2D 風格保留懷舊像素人物</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
